swfupload-rails-authentication
==============================

Demo Rails 2.1 app showing SWFUpload working in tandem with restful-authentication, CSRF protection and attachment_fu.


Requirements
============

Rails 2.1
ImageMagick
mini_magick gem
mime-types gem


Usage
=====

rake db:schema:load
rake db:fixtures:load
script/server


